description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a Full Remote Senior .NET Full\\-stack Developer with \\+5 years of professional experience. The selected candidate will work as part of the development team and report to the project manager and technical leads.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Involve in UI/Logic design and developed markups that follow web standards with a rich user experience;
* Develop front\\-end components and user interfaces using Angular;
* Implement responsive designs for various devices and screen sizes;
* Collaborate with back\\-end developers to integrate front\\-end components with the application;
* Write Low Level Design, Unit Testing Plan and Unit Test case documentation;
* Design, develop, code review, bug\\-fix and test the application;
* Assist in Integration Testing;
* Perform Code optimization and strictly adhere to bank coding standards;
* Assist in any documentation or any artifacts needed for OIS clearance;
* Participate in SCRUM meeting, coordination with onsite and offshore team;
* Timely resolution of issues and root cause analysis of each issue;
* Applied Security Compliance which includes Application and data security assessment and remediation to attain compliance to WB Office Information Security Policies and Standards;
* Ability to work in Agile environment and following best practices;









 Profile:



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* \\+5 years of relevant experience working with Microsoft .NET core 6 using Visual Studio (2022\\), Windows Applications, Console Application \\& C\\#.
* Must have expert\\-level expertise with Microsoft .NET core 8 using Visual Studio (2022\\);
* Expert\\-level competency with C\\# language;
* Expert\\-level expertise with Object Oriented Programming;
* Experience in developing Windows/Desktop Application – WinForms, Console Application \\& C\\#;
* Expert\\-level expertise with SQL Server 2019;
* Experience in developing web applications utilizing HTML5, JQuery, Angular \\+11, CSS3 and JavaScript for UI components;
* Expert\\-level competency in writing SQL Queries, Stored Procedures, ER Diagrams, SQL Profiler, Open Queries, DB Link, etc;
* Experience with ADO.Net, Entity Data model, Entity Framework 4\\.0\\+;
* Experience in application performance monitoring and optimizing;
* Experience using version control and defect tracking systems;
* Experience in REST services;
* Experience in configuration management, release management, versioning and build process;
* Experience in installation, monitoring, upgrade of application executables;
* Experience with Azure Cloud and Azure Devops(VSTS);
* Fluent in English;

